# Best Practices

- Verify information from multiple sources.
- Prefer official websites whenever possible.
- Use precise keywords.
- Keep refining your searches.
- Respect privacy and applicable laws.
- Use Google Dorking only for ethical and legal purposes.

---

# Common Mistakes

- Using very broad keywords.
- Ignoring official sources.
- Not combining operators.
- Assuming every indexed page is accurate.
- Forgetting to verify information.


